('tpl-proposal-v1', 'Standard Proposal', 'proposal', E'GRAVISS MARKETING X [CLIENT NAME]\n[ENGAGEMENT TITLE / SERVICE DESCRIPTION]\n\nThis Proposal is entered into by and between:\n\nClient: [CLIENT NAME] ("Client")\nService Provider: Graviss Marketing, LLC ("Service Provider")\nPrepared by: Jonathan P. Graviss\nDate: [DATE]\n\n1. Introduction\n\n[CLIENT NAME] is [BRIEF DESCRIPTION OF CLIENT — INDUSTRY, POSITION, CURRENT CHALLENGE]. A modern, well-managed digital presence is essential for [RELEVANT BUSINESS GOAL].\n\nGraviss Marketing specializes in [RELEVANT INDUSTRY/SERVICE AREA]. This is not a generic agency engagement — it is an industry-aligned partnership built to deliver results that map directly to your business objectives.\n\nThis proposal outlines [BRIEF DESCRIPTION OF ENGAGEMENT SCOPE].\n\n2. [PRIMARY SERVICE — e.g., Website Development / SEO / Marketing Support]\n\nInvestment: [PRICE] ([One-Time / Monthly])\n\nObjective\n[DESCRIBE THE GOAL OF THIS SERVICE IN 1–2 SENTENCES.]\n\nDeliverables\n\n[DELIVERABLE CATEGORY 1]\n* [Deliverable detail]\n* [Deliverable detail]\n* [Deliverable detail]\n\n[DELIVERABLE CATEGORY 2]\n* [Deliverable detail]\n* [Deliverable detail]\n* [Deliverable detail]\n\n[DELIVERABLE CATEGORY 3]\n* [Deliverable detail]\n* [Deliverable detail]\n* [Deliverable detail]\n\nProcess\n1. [Step 1]\n2. [Step 2]\n3. [Step 3]\n4. [Step 4]\n5. [Step 5]\n\n3. [SECONDARY SERVICE — if applicable]\n\nInvestment: [PRICE] ([One-Time / Monthly])\n\nObjective\n[DESCRIBE THE GOAL OF THIS SERVICE IN 1–2 SENTENCES.]\n\nDeliverables\n\n[DELIVERABLE CATEGORY 1]\n* [Deliverable detail]\n* [Deliverable detail]\n\n[DELIVERABLE CATEGORY 2]\n* [Deliverable detail]\n* [Deliverable detail]\n\n4. [ADDITIONAL SERVICE — if applicable]\n\nInvestment: [PRICE] ([One-Time / Monthly])\n\n[REPEAT STRUCTURE ABOVE AS NEEDED. DELETE SECTION IF NOT APPLICABLE.]\n\n5. Total Investment Summary\n\n| Service | Type | Investment |\n|---------|------|------------|\n| [Service 1] | [One-Time / Monthly] | $[AMOUNT] |\n| [Service 2] | [One-Time / Monthly] | $[AMOUNT] |\n| [Service 3] | [One-Time / Monthly] | $[AMOUNT] |\n| Total Monthly (Post-Launch) | Recurring | $[AMOUNT]/month |\n| [Additional/Optional Service] | As Needed | $[RATE]/hour |\n\n6. Strategic Partnership Value\n\n[1–2 SENTENCES ON WHY GRAVISS MARKETING IS THE RIGHT PARTNER FOR THIS CLIENT SPECIFICALLY. Reference industry knowledge, relevant experience, or shared goals.]\n\nThis proposal is priced to deliver exceptional value relative to market-rate agencies. Our goal is a long-term partnership, not a one-time transaction.\n\n7. Next Steps\n\n1. Review and approve proposal\n2. Execute service agreement via DocuSign\n3. Complete website development questionnaire (link provided by Jonathan) [DELETE IF NOT APPLICABLE]\n4. Schedule intake and discovery meeting\n5. [ADDITIONAL NEXT STEP]\n6. [ADDITIONAL NEXT STEP]\n\nGraviss Marketing — Standing in as your CMO, so you can stay focused on what you do best.', 1, true),

